Node.Notes: With this and the next three iterms, four colors are listed, most likely yarn of four different colors.
Literally worm of scarlet, which produces a scarlet dye.
Probably means the wings of the cherubim coverr the lid in a protective way.
The exact referents of these four terms for vessels is uncertain. See the commentaries. However, it is likely only the last two are used for drink libations.

Node.RefEnglish: {plates of ladles of pitchers of bowls of}
